name: Vessels 115:‘BEETLE’ MECH PILOT
description: When he was bitten by a radioactive beetle on a school trip to the toxic waste dump, Bertie Beetle was amazed to discover that he did not gain beetle superpowers, but instead became incredibly unwell. Undeterred by this setback, Bertie bounced back, became a professional mech pilot and fashioned himself a beetle themed costume to match his mech pilot persona – The Battlin’ Beetle. (Bertie REALLY likes beetles)
